{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Base","content":["Line base of a spring form cake tin (Ø 20 cm) with baking paper.","Place biscuits in mixing bowl and grind <b>8 sec\/speed 10<b>.","Add butter and mix <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>. Spread mixture into prepared cake tin. Use a spoon or your hands to press crumb mixture down firmly to make a compact layer. Place in fridge while making filling."]},{"title":"Filling","content":["Soak gelatine leaves in a bowl of cold water.","Place white chocolate, evaporated milk and caster sugar in mixing bowl then melt <b>7 min\/70°C\/speed 1.5<b>.","Squeeze gelatine leaves to remove excess water then add softened gelatine to mixing bowl and mix <b>10 sec\/speed 4<b>.","Add vanilla extract and cream cheese then mix <b>10 sec\/speed 4<b>.","Add raspberries and gently stir in with spatula, then pour filling into cake tin over biscuit base. Cover with cling film and chill in fridge for at least 6 hours or overnight until set. Serve in slices."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Base","content":["200 g ginger biscuits, halved","80 g butter, diced"]},{"title":"Filling","content":["5 gelatine leaves","water, for soaking gelatine","180 g white chocolate, pieces or callets","200 g light evaporated milk","60 g caster sugar","1 tsp real vanilla extract","500 g cream cheese","250 g raspberries"]}],"id":"r85950","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-pd1Ju7eQ-aw\/XZan1DfWZzI\/AAAAAAAAhEY\/FTsqp_DY87UnXxPNJAaYEQf2Xk9DceEHwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_VlV8yDiLgSTuWKGs.png","title":"White Chocolate and Raspberry Cheesecake","publishedAt":"2015-05-13T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"5.7 g","fat":"33.4 g","uom":"per 1 slice","carbohydrates":"28.4 g","calories":"1828 kJ \/ 437 kcal"},"usefulItems":"spring form tin (Ø 20 cm), baking paper, cling film, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["This cheesecake has to be made ahead to allow time for the filling to set. This makes it a perfect option for when you have guests as everything is done before they arrive!"],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","6h 30m","12 slices"]}